"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The trade-off here is that becoming a node operator or validator in such a network has much higher hardware demands because those blocks make up a ton of data. This could cause a centralization risk as smaller players are essentially priced out from being a node operator or validator.\\n\\nAnyway, no matter how you slice it, more activity inevitably begets higher prices.\\n\\nAnd to bring this idea to a head, if weâ€™re to imagine that blockchain technology is to underpin all financial markets, then the current design landscape means the future is probably going to be expensive.\",\"timestamp\":1638701648,\"title\":\"The trade-off \"},\"digest\":\"7BsVuSYFRJswfEmaMNglmxrBHrh1Oe3mviJ1EddRm_A\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xA2dA61904F8927B64d349A201B0393c7d0B7a59A\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Q5Ibk5os_qDPWqo_GDyOAowZYX876R7R385W5XGVvUs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"LxEXTcyyxpRA_1JF1_B8ag0ZSGqvfuXVPHt5Js12Ys4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BbCrEhCBvAODU9JzRm3Yfxqwj-lpEOFoqTg0p7h6ubV6h2_Bu1f8C1oD97xHWntX03D9RbjtiNA1n9PPHsTYtA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0fc128d86d04fba0af94497c8323e4a4750ae28b198a25323fdcb0526ad4bbc832313d53875e78980d36e6a5d7c3288730468e9256c8404b95764c24769ba7911b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Q5Ibk5os_qDPWqo_GDyOAowZYX876R7R385W5XGVvUs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"LxEXTcyyxpRA_1JF1_B8ag0ZSGqvfuXVPHt5Js12Ys4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"7BsVuSYFRJswfEmaMNglmxrBHrh1Oe3mviJ1EddRm_A\"}"